General.Name: Vereinigte Filzfabriken AG
General.Description: Vereinigte Filzfabriken AG produces and refines felts worldwide. It offers woolen felts, needled felts, cutting and punching services for other materials. The company provides its products under the VFG matproTEX, VFG sealTEX, VFG multiTEX, VFG DESIGNFILZ, VFG PIANO FELT, VFG lineTEC, and VFG weaponCARE brands. It serves piano makers and machine builders, and interior designers and decorators, as well as companies in the automobile, electrical, construction, and steel industries. The company was founded in 1858 and is based in Heidenheim, Germany. Vereinigte Filzfabriken AG is a subsidiary of Wirth Fulda GmbH.
